records.nl_statement: Prove that the intersection of any collection of subspaces of $V$ is a subspace of $V$.
records.lean_header:
import Mathlib

open Fintype Complex Polynomial LinearMap FiniteDimensional Module Module.End
open scoped BigOperators
records.ground_truth:
theorem exercise_1_8 {F V : Type*} [AddCommGroup V] [Field F]
  [Module F V] {ι : Type*} (u : ι → Submodule F V) :
  ∃ U : Submodule F V, (⋂ (i : ι), (u i).carrier) = ↑U :=
